packageId	uuid FK	Yes	References Package.id.
destinationId	uuid FK	Yes	References Destination (Trek).id.
customName	string	No	Override destination name within this package (e.g. 'Kathmandu City Tour').
customDescription	text	No	Override description shown inside the package itinerary for this destination.
durationDays	integer	No	Days allocated to this destination within the package.
sortOrder	integer	No	Display order of destinations within the package.

Package Example	Linked Destinations	Custom Package Price
Golden Triangle Nepal	1. Kathmandu (3 days)  2. Pokhara (3 days)  3. Chitwan (2 days)	$1,200/person (custom price, overrides sum of individual trek prices)
Annapurna & Everest Combo	1. Annapurna Base Camp (10 days)  2. Everest Base Camp (14 days)	$3,500/person with full itinerary and combined inclusions list

